{"id": 502, "genre": 1001, "title": "整理屋子，什么东西你扔的最多？", "description": "Hi，今天你断舍离了吗？", "record_count": 3734, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606004904L3i5tmd80wGaCFBq.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-28T14:02:55Z", "options": [{"id": 10000, "content": "两年没穿的鞋子，衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172511}, {"id": 22785, "content": "回忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288591}, {"id": 9474, "content": "?一开始想着要扔一大堆 最后大部分都舍不得", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169912}, {"id": 9476, "content": "纸张", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170610}, {"id": 9477, "content": "卷子，之前突然心血来潮买的各种小东西，和。。。。。自己（因为实在太乱了自己都住不下去啦(ಥ_ಥ)）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170609}, {"id": 10245, "content": "快递的纸盒子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173626}, {"id": 18437, "content": "曾经买了一箱安全套觉得能用到，结果过期了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 9990, "content": "宝贝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166643}, {"id": 11014, "content": "test", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234951WXCwPTaBpxGA6fK0.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178917}, {"id": 9991, "content": "宝贝和垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166643}, {"id": 9992, "content": "宝贝和垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166643}, {"id": 9737, "content": "废纸orz怎么当时什么都想留着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167116}, {"id": 9483, "content": "我能说为了专门处理票据和纸张，我买了一个碎纸机么?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117070}, {"id": 9484, "content": "卫生纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160915}, {"id": 9996, "content": "垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155133}, {"id": 9997, "content": "本来可以报销，却没有报的过期发票", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109994}, {"id": 9486, "content": "纸巾团团", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163198}, {"id": 10766, "content": "各种纸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177526}, {"id": 9487, "content": "试卷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170635}, {"id": 9488, "content": "什么包装盒啊，矿泉水瓶啊，购物袋啊什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170671}, {"id": 13841, "content": "各种纸张", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211969}, {"id": 9490, "content": "多年前珍而重之的東西，再整理房間時，都不懂為什麼當時不捨得丟……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170705}, {"id": 9746, "content": "很多纸袋，特别喜欢折好留着，就是觉得很好看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170264}, {"id": 9491, "content": "烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139811}, {"id": 10003, "content": "垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156652}, {"id": 9493, "content": "塑料袋，看到飘在家里就不舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129620}, {"id": 9749, "content": "什么都舍不得扔", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120218}, {"id": 9494, "content": "日记本", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131830}, {"id": 9495, "content": "各种以前手机的数据线，充电器啊，旧的衣服鞋子啊，各种小工具……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169522}, {"id": 9753, "content": "钱钱钱，到处到是肮脏钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162056}, {"id": 9498, "content": "卫生纸……又到了一年一度鼻炎犯病的季节", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162968}, {"id": 9754, "content": "平时随手买的小饰品，小挂件，明明买的时候很喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171599}, {"id": 9499, "content": "囤到过期的化妆品→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170761}, {"id": 9500, "content": "地上的垃圾扔的最多。 灰尘次之  即使没有用的发票小纸片也舍不得丢掉  总是用袋子装起来 放好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147096}, {"id": 9501, "content": "无法分类的东西和不好看的东西就扔扔扔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170774}, {"id": 9757, "content": "没用，之前却又舍不得扔的东西…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132556}, {"id": 10015, "content": "用过的电子产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172653}, {"id": 9504, "content": "扔了很多没完全用完的化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170799}, {"id": 9507, "content": "我扔了好多好多书，很难过，但是找不到地方放，也找不到地方捐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138098}, {"id": 9764, "content": "笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171642}, {"id": 9509, "content": "购物小票！旧鞋子、旧衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168351}, {"id": 9510, "content": "各类包装盒，过时的电子产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170869}, {"id": 9766, "content": "精子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171644}, {"id": 9767, "content": "餐巾纸?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171645}, {"id": 10023, "content": "垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157295}, {"id": 14636, "content": "超过三年不用的杂物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224552}, {"id": 9781, "content": "那些之前每次舍不得扔总觉着未来某一刻会用到但其实一直没有机会用到的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171702}, {"id": 20279, "content": "各种小票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269601}, {"id": 9789, "content": "垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171714}, {"id": 9535, "content": "练习册和书还有笔 数不清的...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165319}]}